			<Text>The Conquistador is a multi-purpose unit that is strong both on land and at sea. It is an exceptional scout on land - possessing the scouting 1 promotion. It also has the ability to found new cities that start with extra population, a worker, extra land and some free buildings. In the water, the Conquistador has the defensive embarkation promotion that allows it to defend itself against naval units. It also suffers no penalty when attacking cities, unlike most mounted units.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Requires [COLOR_POSITIVE_TEXT]Empire[ENDCOLOR].</Text>
